I was so enthousiastic when she announced that she's giving a show in Belgium on the 20th of June 2020 ! I was telling everyone I'm finally getting the chance to see her (she doesn't perform that much in Belgium -> the last time was like in 2011) I was walking with my head above the clouds and suddenly my world stops. My sister was like "dude it's your niece's wedding, you can't go see Taylor Swift". I felt heartbroken 'cause it seems like faith is saying that seeing or even meeting her is just not meant for me. I cried that night thinking of the possibility that I'm probably never gonna be see/meet her. This was my one chance life was giving me and the wedding ruins it all :(
